cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.HC

This paper deals with the use of Internet data for medical research and health services, which involves issues related to cybersecurity (cs.CR), information retrieval (cs.IR), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The use of mechanism design to elicit truthful valuations from users also falls under the category of computational complexity (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
